==What is Navigation?== Navigation comprises everything a robot needs to get from point A to point B as efficient as possible without bumping into furniture, walls or people.
This problem breaks down in several sub-problems: *It needs to know [[/Localization|where (Localization)]] it is. *It needs to [[/Collision Avoidance|detect and avoid obstacles (Collision Avoidance)]]. *It needs memory of [[/Mapping|its surroundings (Mapping)]]. *It has to be able to [[/Trajectory Planning|plan a route (Trajectory Planning)]] to point B. *It has to be able to [[/Exploration|explore (Exploration)]] new terrain.
